主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係識打機玩<br />\n<br />\n唔識真人玩，太多牌，又難砌，一砌上手就亂晒龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0ab9d0a56961a27b9193fdfdcde2e1bef79494","tid":98724,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"花唔睇花色 <br />\n淨係鬥第一隻大細 一樣再睇第二隻大細"},{"pid":"455684c8b7a4aaa5c2f92b78f928492a38f8ebea","tid":98724,"uid":35758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/42ud5lqx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F42ud5lqx&h=0192446e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔比我咁出?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 JQKA2<br />\n最大到 10JQKA /A2345<br />\n<br />\n講起巴打一開始打唔好打三張3<br />\n三條其實冇咩用<br />\n如果有多對pair就出5隻<br />\n或者變pair再34567<br />\n<br />\n利申 好少玩"},{"pid":"2cec52f7705754021beb75529679d333113b39e3","tid":98724,"uid":9142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n世紀大戰<br />\nA2345<br />\n23456<br />\n邊個大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一組大，因為有A同2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人理解<br />\n如果JQKA用數字上去睇:<br />\n10<br />\nJ=11<br />\nQ=12<br />\nK=13<br />\nA=14<br />\n2最大姐係15<br />\n<br />\n如果出蛇要順數字細至大<br />\nA2345=14,15,3,4,5<br />\n23456=15,3,4,5,6<br />\n<br />\n所以兩副都唔出得,除非你玩開A同dee可以當1,2"},{"pid":"e996cb007556fe930f90a066bc43722729584d22","tid":98724,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br /